        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1610576651" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16363781763446684097">The first Anne McCaffrey I ever read, and still a favorite. Menolly is a great character, and her adventures are timeless and instantly engaging.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

